<br>
lvl 31-34 gets 5 yellow of main exp<br>
lvl 36-39 gets 10 yellow of main exp<br>
lvl 41-44 gets 15 yellow of main exp<br>
lvl 46-50 gets 20 yellow of main exp<br>
lvl 52-53 gets 5 yellow main and 25 yellow alt exp<br>
lvl 55-58 gets 5 yellow main and 30 yellow alt exp<br>
lvl 60 gets 60 yellow alt exp<br>
<br>
As you can see the extra exp would be cumulative - that is the new &quot;exp&quot; per lvl would be less, and the higher lvl character would already have earned that much exp and alot more.<br>
<br>
ie before you needed a total of 41 million exps to ding 31 now you only need  37 million exps - thats 4 million extra exps that the person would have already earned. Equivalent to about 5 yellows of main xps<br>
<br>
At the Moment it takes about 937 million exp to go from 0 to full main 60. Removing the hell levels removes ALOT of necessary exp. That means a person who has earned 937 million exp already is going to have alot (300 to 500 million) of xtra exp floating around. By fairly redistributing the exp already earned (as in the chart above) long time players of the game will not feel jaded as to the work they have already done. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udycacian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dycacian</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.madco911.com/users/peterroth/theironclaw/sigpics/happyface.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/14/02 11:27:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10258.topic&index=83>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Possible link to hell level removal?</span><hr size=1> looks like I am not the only one who is wondering that <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I for one would STILL like the hell lvls gone even if they didn't compensate.. BUT I would have a sour taste in my mouth for a while due to that Massive amount of time not compensated for.. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uoakfist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>oakfist</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/14/02 11:30:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.c